  ],
  "remarks": "Andrey Guryev is a shareholder of PJSC PhosAgro and the President of the Russian Association of Fertiliser Producers (RAPU). Furthermore, he is a Member of the Bureau of the Board of the Russian Union of Industrialists and Entrepreneurs. As such, he is actively involved in facilitating the export of fertilisers from Russia, in close cooperation with the Russian Government. Russia is the largest exporter of fertilisers in the world and PhosAgro is one of the leading producers of phosphate-based fertilisers.",
